title: 820-00164 no post, image, dong - turns on
message:
Hi guys,
Another MacBook Air - clean, no liquid, absolutely clean board, first person working on it, 820-00164 11" turns on sees battery, does SMC reset if keys pressed, no post, dong, image - doesn't react if trying PRAM, 
Checked voltages around U6100 and missing SPI_MLB_CLK, traced back to R6121 -> R6111 Pin1 receives it from U0500, any signals I can check for it in order to shoot out clock signal?
Thank you
